ADDITIONAL DISCLAIMER

This software contains an AI-synthesized persona ("Brain of Naval") derived
from public long-form interviews of Naval Ravikant, and optionally a secondary
persona derived from public dialogues of Kapil Gupta.

The Brain of Naval and related personas:

  - Are NOT affiliated with, authorized by, or endorsed by Naval Ravikant,
    Kapil Gupta, or any other referenced individual.
  - Are an artistic and practical synthesis for personal reference only.
  - Do not reproduce any copyrighted transcript in full; they distill patterns,
    vocabulary, and reasoning structures observed across public interviews.
  - Should not be used to claim, imply, or represent the views of the source
    individuals on any specific matter.

Users are responsible for their own decisions. The personas are not counselors,
advisors, therapists, lawyers, or fiduciaries. Nothing produced by this
software constitutes professional advice.
